| **Alpha fade opacity** | `ShaderPrimitiveSorter::Entry` — `ShaderPrimitiveSorter.cpp:707–708`, `742` | Set at add for fading appearances (`SkeletalAppearance2.cpp:1777`) | **Per draw entry** | `m_fadeState`, `m_fadeFraction` per appearance |
| **Representative color** (`m_representativeColor`) | `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive` — `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.h:163`, `computeRepresentativeColor()` `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp:2543+` | Lazily computed mutable cache | **Per shader-primitive instance** | Customization hues / main texture color |
| **Box extent** (`m_boxExtent`) | `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive` — `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.h:165`, updated in `fillVertexBuffer` / hard-skin path `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp:1820` | Updated during skinning (every other frame for soft skin, `SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp:1834`) | **Per shader-primitive instance** | Skinned bounds follow pose |
